This Investment Analysis Function provides several key capabilities for luxury watch investors and collectors:

Investment Rating System: Calculates an investment score (0-100) based on multiple factors:

Historical performance data
Market liquidity
Supply constraints
Demand drivers
Brand strength


Data Management:

Stores and updates model-specific data
Tracks user's price points and notes
Maintains historical performance metrics


Price Trend Analysis:

Calculates price trends if multiple data points exist
Provides annualized returns
Shows total percentage change


Investment Recommendations:

Generates specific recommendations based on score
Categories range from "Strong Buy" to "Avoid as Investment"
Includes explanatory factors for the rating


User-Friendly Features:

Allows adding notes and price points
Supports reference number specificity
Maintains a knowledge base of watch models



This function would be the core of your MindStudio luxury watch investment advisor application, allowing collectors to get informed investment analysis for specific watch models without the complexity of the full tracking system.
